586
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:07,670
I saw you not long ago.

587
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:09,960
If I talk with you again,

588
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,030
Pei might get jealous,

589
00:29:11,030 --> 00:29:12,110
saying I've been

590
00:29:12,110 --> 00:29:12,950
monopolizing you.

591
00:29:13,020 --> 00:29:13,960
Pei, on the other hand,

592
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,430
