595
00:29:18,510 --> 00:29:19,480
Yes, yes, Qian.

596
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:22,390
Alright.

597
00:29:22,390 --> 00:29:23,830
I'll accompany Pei tonight

598
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:25,430
and go find you tomorrow.

599
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:27,430
(It's hard to bring him down,)

600
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:28,860
(but however difficult,)

601
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,150
(I'll make sure he pays the price.)

602
00:29:32,790 --> 00:29:35,110
Si has endured such humiliation.

603
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:37,430
How can we keep quiet?

604
00:29:37,840 --> 00:29:39,960
Even if I risk my life,

605
00:29:40,070 --> 00:29:41,030
I will never

606
00:29:41,030 --> 00:29:42,720
let Cao Xingyu have it easy.

607
00:29:42,840 --> 00:29:44,080
Let's go, Si.

608
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,630
Let's report to the authorities.

609
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:47,310
Brother, you can't go.

610
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:49,320
No one steps out of this door.

611
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:52,520
Grandmother, what do you mean?

612
00:29:54,230 --> 00:29:56,520
Brother, stop causing a scene.

613
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:57,960
If this continues,

614
00:29:57,960 --> 00:30:00,240
Si's reputation will be ruined.

615
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:01,710
How will she ever hold her head high

616
00:30:01,710 --> 00:30:03,830
at Duke An's Mansion?

617
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:09,200
You're just trying to save
your daughter's face.

618
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:10,590
Is your daughter's face

619
00:30:10,790 --> 00:30:13,350
