Si.

643
00:31:08,840 --> 00:31:10,240
Sorry for my incapability.

644
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:12,920
I've asked many girls

645
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,390
who've been wronged by him,

646
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:16,240
but no one is willing

647
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:17,480
to come forward as a witness.

648
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:19,960
Many of the girls

649
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:20,920
