Si.

667
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:44,480
Qiao.

668
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:46,760
Why haven't you rested yet?

669
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:48,480
Si.

670
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:50,350
Can I sleep with you?

671
00:32:51,790 --> 00:32:53,390
I'm used to sleeping alone.

672
00:32:53,990 --> 00:32:55,160
I'm a bit uncomfortable

673
