How about this?

683
00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:19,240
You sleep inside.

684
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:22,590
Si, I'm used to sleeping on the outside.

685
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:24,640
I didn't expect you to have

686
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:26,190
