693
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,150
(And)

694
00:33:39,230 --> 00:33:41,150
(Qiao isn't usually so insistent.)

695
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:42,350
(What's going on today?)

696
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:45,960
(Qian and her husband are targeting me.)

697
00:33:46,710 --> 00:33:48,350
(If Jiang Qiao is always with me,)

698
00:33:48,790 --> 00:33:50,430
(it'll be dangerous for her.)

699
00:33:51,470 --> 00:33:53,110
(Since they can hurt me,)

700
00:33:53,710 --> 00:33:54,690
(they absolutely won't)

701
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:56,080
(show mercy to Jiang Qiao.)

702
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:58,590
(Only tonight.)

703
00:33:58,790 --> 00:34:00,630
(I can't let her cling to me tomorrow.)

704
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:03,000
(As for tonight...)

705
00:35:19,990 --> 00:35:21,560
Nuo, light the lamp.

706
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:23,110
Nuo, Aman, light the lamp.

707
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:24,960
Hurry and light the lamp.

708
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:40,520
Alright, you can leave now.

709
00:35:41,030 --> 00:35:42,040
Stay outside.

710
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:43,760
Yes.

711
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:51,560
Si.

712
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:54,110
Did you see him?

713
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:56,480
Cao Xingyu is a beast.

714
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:02,390
Qiao,

715
00:36:04,190 --> 00:36:05,840
