716
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:08,000
Si, we'll return tomorrow.

717
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,150
Qian will definitely

718
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,000
try to stop us.

719
00:36:10,190 --> 00:36:11,590
Is she going to physically stop us

720
00:36:11,590 --> 00:36:12,520
from leaving?

721
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:26,670
Si.

722
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:29,990
Qian...

723
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:35,230
Si, let's go back tomorrow.

724
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,550
- Okay?
- No.

725
00:36:36,550 --> 00:36:38,190
Right now, in their eyes,

726
00:36:38,510 --> 00:36:39,750
you're an outsider.

727
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:41,150
If you demand

728
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:42,310
to leave tomorrow morning...

729
00:36:42,550 --> 00:36:44,230
As you sleep with me tonight,

730
00:36:44,990 --> 00:36:46,150
and that beast comes by,

731
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:47,360
they'll surely think

732
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:48,710
you've discovered something.

733
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:52,270
Qiao, give me some time.

734
00:36:52,670 --> 00:36:53,670
I'll go check it out.

735
00:36:54,070 --> 00:36:54,920
I'll go with you.

736
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:55,760
It's fine.

737
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:22,280
The heir went out last night,

738
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:23,720
and he looked off when he came back.

739
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:24,760
He may be upset

740
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:26,150
so he came for her.

741
00:37:26,470 --> 00:37:28,110
She's unlucky

742
00:37:28,110 --> 00:37:29,230
and is meant to die today.

743
00:37:43,550 --> 00:37:45,040
Anzi, help me. Hurry.

744
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:53,570
I'll go get the spade.

745
00:37:55,690 --> 00:37:56,880
It has nothing to do with me.

746
00:37:56,930 --> 00:37:57,980
Don't come looking for me.

747
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,670
It was the heir who killed you.

748
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,480
You'll be buried soon.

749
00:38:03,470 --> 00:38:05,080
One of the spades is missing.

750
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,190
Did someone take it?

751
00:38:07,190 --> 00:38:08,230
How could that happen?

752
00:38:08,590 --> 00:38:10,190
The gardener tidied up for us earlier.

753
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,550
After we scolded them,

754
00:38:11,550 --> 00:38:12,920
no one dared to touch it again.

755
00:38:13,150 --> 00:38:14,480
Get a hoe. Hurry.

756
00:38:24,470 --> 00:38:25,310
What's wrong?

757
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:28,270
Her hand...

758
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:32,630
There's a ghost.

759
00:39:24,170 --> 00:39:25,070
Don't blame me.

760
00:39:25,070 --> 00:39:26,630
You shouldn't have seen this.

761
00:39:26,630 --> 00:39:27,630
Do we have to kill her?

762
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:28,840
Should we give her to the heir?

763
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:30,080
If she doesn't die, we will.

764
00:39:30,280 --> 00:39:31,120
Hurry up and help.

765
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:32,160
Hurry.

766
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:34,120
(I can't die.)

767
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:35,560
(I can't die.)

768
00:39:58,110 --> 00:39:59,000
Yu Qi?

769
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:02,560
Yu what? Hurry and run.

770
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:14,040
Why are you here?

771
00:40:16,110 --> 00:40:17,280
Looks like Commandant Yu

772
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:18,710
isn't good at investigating.

773
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:20,510
You didn't even know

774
00:40:20,510 --> 00:40:21,920
Marquis Changxing's heir

775
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:23,080
is my son-in-law.

776
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:24,710
You're still making jokes.

777
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:26,670
If I hadn't arrived in time,

778
00:40:26,670 --> 00:40:28,360
you wouldn't have had
the chance to joke.

779
00:40:29,030 --> 00:40:30,520
Then why are you here?

780
00:40:30,890 --> 00:40:32,350
I'm investigating the missing cases.

781
00:40:32,590 --> 00:40:33,960
I think it's related to Cao Xingyu.

782
00:40:35,190 --> 00:40:37,310
Did he do anything to you?

783
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:40,630
What should he have done to me?

784
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:43,640
That's good.

785
00:40:44,470 --> 00:40:46,560
Why do they want to kill you?

786
00:40:51,150 --> 00:40:52,520
If you want to live, don't move.

787
00:40:53,110 --> 00:40:53,950
Listen carefully.

788
00:40:53,990 --> 00:40:55,920
Tonight, after you finish your work,

789
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,840
