in the flower bushes.

794
00:41:16,190 --> 00:41:17,190
I saw them

795
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:18,870
killing and burying the body.

796
00:41:19,030 --> 00:41:19,870
I suspect

797
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:21,440
there may be more victims.

798
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,400
They are so bold.

799
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:26,750
Businesswomen often wear
copper hairpins.

800
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:28,400
Tomorrow, I will go verify.

801
00:41:29,190 --> 00:41:30,150
If Ms. Xiu's daughter

802
00:41:30,150 --> 00:41:31,000
really has died,

803
00:41:31,470 --> 00:41:32,800
- what should she do?
- Enough.

804
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,780
Stop worrying about others.

805
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:36,150
Worry about yourself for a moment.

806
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:37,640
It's too dangerous here. Come with me.

807
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:38,990
Yu Qi,

808
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:40,950
I can't leave.

809
00:41:41,510 --> 00:41:43,000
Tell me why.

810
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:43,920
Why can't you leave?

811
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:45,190
If I leave now,

812
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,510
Cao Xingyu will think of ways

813
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:47,520
to deal with my family.

814
00:41:47,990 --> 00:41:49,360
My second sister is his wife.

815
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:50,470
Although...

816
00:41:52,110 --> 00:41:53,270
Although it was her

817
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:55,110
who brought me here...

818
00:41:55,300 --> 00:41:56,510
There's also my third sister.

819
00:41:56,510 --> 00:41:57,510
She's so weak,

820
00:41:57,510 --> 00:41:59,040
yet she's still trying to protect me.

821
00:41:59,220 --> 00:42:00,110
And my fifth sister...

822
00:42:00,110 --> 00:42:00,960
- Wait.
- She...

823
00:42:03,070 --> 00:42:05,000
What do you mean?

824
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,470
Your second sister brought you here?

825
00:42:11,240 --> 00:42:12,720
No, it's too dangerous here.

826
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:14,080
I'll take you home now.

827
00:42:14,240 --> 00:42:16,430
After we get back,
I'll report to the Capital Security.

828
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:17,680
Yu Qi,

829
00:42:18,070 --> 00:42:19,040
calm down.

830
00:42:19,590 --> 00:42:21,190
Marquis Changxing has imperial favor,

831
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,000
and Cao Xingyu is his only son.

832
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:24,230
I know very well

833
00:42:24,550 --> 00:42:25,560
