into thin air.

844
00:42:40,990 --> 00:42:42,110
What do you mean?

845
00:42:43,110 --> 00:42:44,110
Have you already

846
00:42:44,110 --> 00:42:44,960
done something?

847
00:42:45,470 --> 00:42:46,630
Anyway, you must trust me.

848
00:42:46,630 --> 00:42:47,590
I really can't leave.

849
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:48,880
If I leave now,

850
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:50,150
it will only alert them,

851
00:42:50,150 --> 00:42:51,870
